Typing in a URL and hitting Enter, although it may appear simple, sets off a complicated chain of events that includes load balancers, web servers, application servers, firewalls, DNS requests, TCP/IP connections, and databases. This complex system guarantees that you will be able to instantly, safely, and effortlessly access the webpage you want. It is possible to gain insights into the amazing engineering and technology that support the modern web by comprehending this trip.
Author: Tech-Doc
